Summary of Amendments Adopted by House
The Committee Amendments Proposed by House Committee on Education to the
original bill:
1. Grant authority to override the council's denial to BESE instead of the
superintendent.
2. Authorize BESE to call a special meeting to consider overriding a denial.
3. Authorize BESE to delegate its authority to the board president.
4. Provide that if an appellant submits a request to override a denial, BESE or the
board president shall render a decision within 30 days of receipt of the request.
